AnalysisDataSource.SNAPSHOT_DATA: Save data snapshot, display snapshot data each time

AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.PROGRESS: Track project, sprint, or assignee work progress. Help teams evaluate task scheduling and work efficiency.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.BURNDOWN: Track the likelihood of completing all work within the planned time. Help teams monitor progress and respond accordingly.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.WORKLOAD: Understand team workload, evaluate workload and actual workload deviations. Help teams ensure reasonable workload distribution.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.OVERDUE_ASSESSMENT: Evaluate tasks that are not completed on time, enabling teams to adjust strategies and optimize resource allocation. Help teams identify potential risks and bottlenecks.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.BUGS: Evaluate issues in the system that do not meet expectations. Help teams understand design flaws, implementation problems, or insufficient testing.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.HANDLING_EFFICIENCY: Evaluate the frequency of repeated task handling, revealing poor completion quality issues. Help teams identify quality bottlenecks and adjust work standards in a timely manner.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.CORE_KPI: Evaluate key performance indicators such as number of tasks, total workload, overdue items, and bugs. Facilitate quick performance evaluation of R&D teams.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.FAILURES: Evaluate the number of defects, their severity distribution, and resolution timeliness. Help teams analyze failure causes and track resolution status.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.BACKLOG_TASKS: Summarize unfinished tasks and workload, evaluate whether completion time has overdue risks. Help teams identify overdue risks and manage progress.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.RECENT_DELIVERY: Evaluate recently completed tasks and deliverables. Help teams identify gaps between completed work items and expected goals, thereby adjusting strategies and resource allocation timely.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.LEAD_TIME: Evaluate the time required to complete tasks and the distribution of processing cycles. Help teams monitor the efficiency and stability of the delivery process.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.UNPLANNED_TASKS: Evaluate unplanned tasks that appear during execution, understand their impact on overall progress and resource allocation. Help teams identify interference factors and avoid risks.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.TASK_GROWTH_TREND: Evaluate the number of new tasks added within a specific time period and their impact on project progress. Help teams adjust strategies timely to cope with the continuously growing work demands.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.RESOURCE_CREATION: Evaluate the creation of various resources such as backlogs, sprints, tasks, and meetings. Help teams understand the effective utilization and contribution of resources.
AnalysisTaskTemplateDesc.CUSTOM_DEFINITION: Perform custom status or time-series analysis on key indicators. Help teams gain in-depth understanding of specific data changes, statuses, and distributions.

AnalysisCaseTemplateDesc.SUBMITTED_BUGS: Evaluate the bug submission status of testers. Help teams understand test hit rate, analyze case design and functional implementation deficiencies.
AnalysisCaseTemplateDesc.TESTING_EFFICIENCY: Evaluate the frequency of repeated case testing, revealing poor completion quality issues. Help teams identify quality bottlenecks and adjust work standards in a timely manner.
AnalysisCaseTemplateDesc.CORE_KPI: Evaluate key performance indicators such as number of cases, total workload, overdue items, and reviews. Facilitate quick performance evaluation of testing teams.
AnalysisCaseTemplateDesc.REVIEW_EFFICIENCY: Evaluate the efficiency of the test case review process. Help teams optimize testing strategies and ensure high-quality software delivery.
AnalysisCaseTemplateDesc.BACKLOG_CASES: Summarize unfinished cases and workload, evaluate whether completion time has overdue risks. Help teams identify overdue risks and manage progress.
AnalysisCaseTemplateDesc.RECENT_DELIVERY: Evaluate recently completed cases and deliverables. Help teams identify gaps between completed work items and expected goals, thereby adjusting strategies and resource allocation timely.
AnalysisCaseTemplateDesc.LEAD_TIME: Evaluate the time required to complete cases and the distribution of processing cycles. Help teams monitor the efficiency and stability of the delivery process.

AnalysisCaseTemplateDesc.RESOURCE_CREATION: Evaluate the creation of various resources such as plans, cases, reviews, and baselines. Help teams understand the effective utilization and contribution of resources.
AnalysisCaseTemplateDesc.CUSTOM_DEFINITION: Perform custom status or time-series analysis on key indicators. Help teams gain in-depth understanding of specific data changes, statuses, and distributions.
